        "subject": "LU-0000 tests: EC probe, round-trip checks, fallocate",
        "message": "LU-0000 tests: EC probe, round-trip checks, fallocate\n\n- Add a single EC capability probe and gate IO tests with\n  skip when unsupported\n- Treat EC creation failures as errors when EC is supported\n- Strengthen negative tests with specific lfs error substrings\n- Normalize fallocate handling with check_set_fallocate and\n  skip_env\n- Use existing layout verification helpers consistently\n\nTest-Parameters: forjanitoronly\nSigned-off-by: Patrick Farrell <pfarrell@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: Ie29155a93e0fddcb4b103d67f4022dafe250f490\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
